{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>Project Overview</h2>\n<p>As part of modernizing boston.gov, we're slowly going through the legacy web applications we have left on cityofboston.gov and moving each over to <a href=\"https://www.boston.gov/\">boston.gov</a>.</p>\n<p>We thought it was important to make the information our boards and commissions look-up tool displays easier to find on boston.gov, so we updated the app and wrote about the changes and process on the Digital Team's blog: <a href=\"https://www.boston.gov/news/boards-and-commissions-get-deserved-bostongov-facelift\">Boards and Commissions get a deserved boston.gov facelift</a>.</p>\n<hr>\n<div class=\"imageBlock\">\n    <div>\n        <a href=\"https://www.boston.gov/news/boards-and-commissions-get-deserved-bostongov-facelift\">\n            <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 900px;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 52.361111111111114%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n    <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Boards and Commissions get a deserved boston.gov facelift\" title src=\"/static/165167fee25547fee067658dc230e718/48396/boards-commissions-screen-shot.png\" srcset=\"/static/165167fee25547fee067658dc230e718/39d7a/boards-commissions-screen-shot.png 225w,\n/static/165167fee25547fee067658dc230e718/d45f3/boards-commissions-screen-shot.png 450w,\n/static/165167fee25547fee067658dc230e718/48396/boards-commissions-screen-shot.png 900w,\n/static/165167fee25547fee067658dc230e718/14262/boards-commissions-screen-shot.png 1350w,\n/static/165167fee25547fee067658dc230e718/c1e46/boards-commissions-screen-shot.png 1800w,\n/static/165167fee25547fee067658dc230e718/83e3a/boards-commissions-screen-shot.png 2700w,\n/static/165167fee25547fee067658dc230e718/cbb2b/boards-commissions-screen-shot.png 2880w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\">\n  </span>\n        </a>\n    </div>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Boards and Commissions","myRole":"Product Manager"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/projects/boards-and-commissions/"}}